_______________________________________________________________________________
"Reduce Weight"    
        This power allows the psionicist to alter the pattern of an
        object in such a way as to condense and compact it.  It
        works once per item and reduces the item's weight
        permanently by a random amount influenced, but not determined,
        by guild level. 
 
SP Cost:  75		Guild Level:  7		Potential Points:  2
 
Command:  reduce <object>
